DataElement.preferredName: Disease or Disorder Evaluation Identifier java.lang.Long
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Any abnormal condition of the body or mind that causes discomfort, dysfunction, or distress to the person affected or those in contact with the person. The term is often used broadly to include injuries, disabilities, syndromes, symptoms, deviant behaviors, and atypical variations of structure and function.:Systematic, objective appraisal of the significance, effectiveness, and impact of activities or condition according to specified objectives and criteria._One or more characters used to identify, name, or characterize the nature, properties, or contents of a thing._Generic value domain for a primitive java dataype that is a long integer (64-bit two's complement).
